<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Enrolled in {{courseName}}</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6 0%, #7c3aed 100%);
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .header p {
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        
        .greeting {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1f2937;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .course-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #faf5ff 0%, #f3e8ff 100%);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #8b5cf6;
        }
        
        .course-title {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #5b21b6;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .course-details {
            display: grid;
            gap: 15px;
        }
        
        .detail-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .detail-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #374151;
            width: 120px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        
        .detail-value {
            color: #4b5563;
            flex: 1;
        }
        
        .schedule-info {
            background-color: #e0e7ff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .schedule-info h4 {
            color: #3730a3;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .date-range {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1e1b4b;
        }
        
        .cta-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 40px 0;
        }
        
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6 0%, #7c3aed 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 16px 32px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease;
        }
        
        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        
        .next-steps {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .next-steps h3 {
            color: #1f2937;
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .steps-list {
            list-style: none;
            counter-reset: step-counter;
        }
        
        .steps-list li {
            counter-increment: step-counter;
            padding: 12px 0;
            color: #4b5563;
            padding-left: 40px;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .steps-list li:before {
            content: counter(step-counter);
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: 12px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6 0%, #7c3aed 100%);
            color: white;
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .message {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #4b5563;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }
        
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .footer a {
            color: #8b5cf6;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .content {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            
            .header {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
            
            .course-card {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            
            .course-title {
                font-size: 20px;
            }
            
            .detail-item {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 5px;
            }
            
            .detail-label {
                width: auto;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>ðŸŽ“ Course Enrollment</h1>
            <p>Welcome to your new learning journey</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">
                Hello{{#if recipientName}} {{recipientName}}{{/if}},
            </div>
            
            <div class="message">
                Congratulations! You have successfully enrolled in your new course. We're excited to have you join us on this learning journey.
            </div>
            
            <div class="course-card">
                <div class="course-title">{{courseName}}</div>
                
                <div class="course-details">
                    {{#if courseDescription}}
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <span class="detail-label">Description:</span>
                        <span class="detail-value">{{courseDescription}}</span>
                    </div>
                    {{/if}}
                    
                    {{#if instructorName}}
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <span class="detail-label">Instructor:</span>
                        <span class="detail-value">{{instructorName}}</span>
                    </div>
                    {{/if}}
                </div>
                
                {{#if startDate}}
                <div class="schedule-info">
                    <h4>Course Schedule</h4>
                    <div class="date-range">
                        {{formatDate startDate 'short'}}{{#if endDate}} - {{formatDate endDate 'short'}}{{/if}}
                    </div>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
            </div>
            
            <div class="cta-section">
                <a href="{{courseUrl}}" class="cta-button">Access Your Course</a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="next-steps">
                <h3>What's Next?</h3>
                <ol class="steps-list">
                    <li>Review the course syllabus and schedule</li>
                    <li>Complete any prerequisite assessments</li>
                    <li>Join course discussions and forums</li>
                    <li>Start working through the course materials</li>
                    <li>Reach out to your instructor with any questions</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
            
            <div class="message">
                You now have access to all course materials, assignments, and resources. We recommend starting with the course overview to familiarize yourself with the curriculum.
            </div>
            
            <div class="message">
                <strong>Pro Tips for Success:</strong>
                <ul style="margin-left: 20px; margin-top: 10px;">
                    <li>Set aside dedicated time for studying each week</li>
                    <li>Participate actively in discussions and forums</li>
                    <li>Don't hesitate to ask questions if you're stuck</li>
                    <li>Connect with fellow students for peer learning</li>
                    <li>Take advantage of all available resources</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="message">
                We're excited to support you throughout your learning journey. Let's achieve great things together!
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Need help? Contact us at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a></p>
            <p>
                {{companyName}} | 
                {{#if unsubscribeUrl}}<a href="{{unsubscribeUrl}}">Unsubscribe</a>{{/if}}
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 